  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Scaling Up Productive Water</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Access to affordable productive water technologies disseminated by International Development Enterprises (IDE) through setting up sustainable local supply chains have proven to impact incomes and water productivity of over 300&apos;000 small farmers so far. The project in phase 2 will make the regional programs sustainable and allow them to grow further, building strong linkages with financial services. It will develop and disseminate tools to use water in an efficient and sustainable way, and make suitable technologies and dissemination approaches available for replication globally.</narrative>
  </description>
